{"tid":1562490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果敵人清文宣 敵人就會預計大家係同一個地方貼文宣","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T03:31:47.000Z","uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8516ed1c8f1211de6f5fa0c07128552107569b","tid":1562490,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"不過如果大家識得改為係另一個未有文宣既地方貼文宣<br />\n就比較難捉摸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbbf8fdef455420a6fef123d48030f4c8d3b400","tid":1562490,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3bb92653b582e75733c4863c1dad915fd621803","tid":1562490,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b430c845e2d31c97f91282964d7e235719ad3a39","tid":1562490,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dNzC1p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dNzC1p.png&h=5baec1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcjBRmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcjBRmp.png&h=e29bbbda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dKvabmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdKvabmt.png&h=ed1fd2c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71447cf7a27b7a2a68e4df6855db78a776a58d36","tid":1562490,"uid":67702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"文宣組求下你哋睇下<br />\n1.加多啲資訊性內容<br />\n恥笑圖，毅進仔歌詞 啲老人家真係睇唔明架<br />\n而且恥笑圖無助建立我哋嘅形象<br />\n建議文宣可以加少少字<br />\n放多啲黑警暴行出黎<br />\n資料舊都唔怕<br />\n老人家冇記性 長氣啲都唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n2.文宣要傓情啲！摧淚啲！<br />\n雖然仇恨可以激起民憤<br />\n但有啲人以為我哋為反而反<br />\n而傓情更加可以吸納一班中間派人士<br />\nE.g. 831太子站 3位失蹤人士下落不明<br />\n各位爸爸媽媽可以還佢地公道嗎？<br />\n<br />\n3.澄清文<br />\n對家藍屍不斷抹黑我哋<br />\n唔上網既公公婆婆係唔知真相架<br />\n一定要澄清！<br />\nE.g. 屈我地有女仔比義士屌<br />\n我地就貼番張圖<br />\n一大隻字寫住<br />\n藍屍拎越南咸片黎屈前線 之類"},{"pid":"f8741c9ae1154cc8da529df933e35024df150c48","tid":1562490,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong>兵者，詭道也</strong><br />\n用兵之道在於千變萬化，出其不意<br />\n<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊<br />\n<strong>＜孫子兵法 始計篇＞</strong><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"d192a1fedf442248e70fda874fbc2c5ef27ddfdf","tid":1562490,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1ce3d924078932c12e75c419b21463deef58b2","tid":1562490,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f1ba866c417bb5e9a3d17440d3e1ea9be6d535","tid":1562490,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0248a4a5a4b6a84578f2a03ad3cb02c26b8d242d","tid":1562490,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}